d658e07656db6a7e6374f6fd6f4637ed1f/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f24736b5f6924" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/2722b0d658e07656db6a7e6374f6fd6f4637ed1f/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f24736b5f6924" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$sk_i$" /></a>.</li>
<li>Then for a time bound <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/f3567efd1415deb104c845af0c76345ec56cf17e/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f2425354344656c746124" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/f3567efd1415deb104c845af0c76345ec56cf17e/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f2425354344656c746124" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$%5CDelta$" /></a>, the validators gossip these lotteries with each other. Each validator collects the top 3 minimum-value lottery in the gossip process.</li>
