http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$%5Cpi_%7B0,e%7D$" /></a> and divide nodes into buckets of size <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/db8cad5ff4351b3b5a3d89cfb69be9a2408873ad/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246b24" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/db8cad5ff4351b3b5a3d89cfb69be9a2408873ad/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246b24" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$k$" /></a> . In this way, the node to swap-batch mapping is determined.</li>
