<p><strong>Output:</strong> the micro state block <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/eca7374826c7bd221f9baeea2358e74f27e31b3b/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246d73625f2537426a2c6525374424" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/eca7374826c7bd221f9baeea2358e74f27e31b3b/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246d73625f2537426a2c6525374424" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$msb_%7Bj,e%7D$" /></a> for <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/95d1dadc5b0cd64ce7b09ac4b11e57e4303f47c5/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246a24" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/95d1dadc5b0cd64ce7b09ac4b11e57e4303f47c5/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246a24" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$j$" /></a> in <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/93f28da07b25b006ffd29695506289a95618410f/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246524" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/93f28da07b25b006ffd29695506289a95618410f/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246524" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$e$" /></a></p>
<ol>
<li>When the epoch <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/93f28da07b25b006ffd29695506289a95618410f/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246524" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/93f28da07b25b006ffd29695506289a95618410f/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246524" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$e$" /></a> ends, the shard leader stores all transactions of <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/93f28da07b25b006ffd29695506289a95618410f/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246524" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/93f28da07b25b006ffd29695506289a95618410f/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246524" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$e$" /></a> in a Merkle tree [14].</li>
<li>The shard leader hashes the Merkle tree’s root, denoted by <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/aeea30c5eccc22d4dac8e0aeb914a2a9df7b9c35/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246824" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/aeea30c5eccc22d4dac8e0aeb914a2a9df7b9c35/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246824" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$h$" /></a>, and puts <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/aeea30c5eccc22d4dac8e0aeb914a2a9df7b9c35/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246824" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/aeea30c5eccc22d4dac8e0aeb914a2a9df7b9c35/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246824" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$h$" /></a> in <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c6a2139fd1d1906670c5c4d9864a9a7e0809b559/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f24486561646572286d73625f2537426a2c652537442924" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c6a2139fd1d1906670c5c4d9864a9a7e0809b559/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f24486561646572286d73625f2537426a2c652537442924" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$Header(msb_%7Bj,e%7D)$" /></a>.</li>
<li>Validators run consensus on the <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c6a2139fd1d1906670c5c4d9864a9a7e0809b559/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f24486561646572286d73625f2537426a2c652537442924" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c6a2139fd1d1906670c5c4d9864a9a7e0809b559/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f24486561646572286d73625f2537426a2c652537442924" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$Header(msb_%7Bj,e%7D)$" /></a>, while there is not any regular blocks pending.</li>
<li>If the correctness of <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c6a2139fd1d1906670c5c4d9864a9a7e0809b559/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f24486561646572286d73625f2537426a2c652537442924" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c6a2139fd1d1906670c5c4d9864a9a7e0809b559/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f24486561646572286d73625f2537426a2c652537442924" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$Header(msb_%7Bj,e%7D)$" /></a> is verified, the shard leader stores the approved header in the shard’s blockchain.</li>
<li>At the end of epoch <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/d8d6b39fcd4fe6c1b801c45ad2e9f0e14f439f77/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f24652b3124" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/d8d6b39fcd4fe6c1b801c45ad2e9f0e14f439f77/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f24652b3124" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$e+1$" /></a>, all the nodes drop the body of <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/fa9f94414aa34c0d09d92e87d1575785a118f2c6/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246d73625f2537426a2c652d3125374424" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/fa9f94414aa34c0d09d92e87d1575785a118f2c6/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246d73625f2537426a2c652d3125374424" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$msb_%7Bj,e-1%7D$" /></a> and keep the regular blocks of <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/93f28da07b25b006ffd29695506289a95618410f/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246524" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/93f28da07b25b006ffd29695506289a95618410f/687474703a2f2f6c617465782e636f6465636f67732e636f6d2f6769662e6c617465783f246524" alt="" data-canonical-src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?$e$" /></a>.</li>
</ol>
